*   **`design-system.css` (`:root`)**: This is your **single source of truth**. It defines your core design tokens (colors, shadows, etc.) as native CSS custom properties. This is ideal because these variables are now framework-agnostic and can be used by anything, including vanilla CSS, JavaScript, or other libraries.
